channel.title: Missing class8.java file in client :s
channel.description: Hey guys, i got a garboscape server and client. But im missing the class8.java file in the client so i cant add dragon claws etc. When i take a class8.java file from another server and add it then the godsword and saradomin sword changes the model to like black dagger and exalibur.. If i cant get the right class8.java file is it a way to change the models back again after adding the class8.java file?
